{"tid":1691451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈阻膠仲衰過藍絲","createTime":"2019-11-03T16:04:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:59.000Z","uid":238500,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53612a9aef48817e6826942dca344eaf808768db","tid":1691451,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"先唔講佢傷左2定3個人/手足先<br />\n見到趙家賢個耳仔甩左一半出嚟<br />\n竟然仲有人去保護個兇手<br />\n大佬啊11月啦 唔係覺得popo會執法啊<br />\n佢地內心不知覺得啲人係抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n下次召喚神獸 唔好打頭 起碼打下手腳關節<br />\n唔好比佢好似今日咁掙扎走<br />\n然後仲要賤到夾硬扯手足幫佢擋傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n怕大家唔記得血的教訓<br />\n我點都要post番張相提醒大家<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nPDCban.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnPDCban.jpg&h=3cd65942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n反正而家都只會放生呢堆渣滓藍絲<br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好阻手足召喚神獸啦 針對手腳比較有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"73540c9bfe1eb15c566896376c55c49c32888783","tid":1691451,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:05:16.000Z","msg":"自己力推"},{"pid":"b008508c7f3099b277548b69bf65be189064b368","tid":1691451,"uid":120627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c6b98d57bb9398772f743a1645f228902cc05f9","tid":1691451,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"利申睇到呆撚左 真係搞唔掂點解可以有咁痴線嘅事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ecd9905d4324a866a70a0ed041397d7c03fc5d","tid":1691451,"uid":297569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"希望大家嚟睇下 時刻保持冷靜同分析能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［警世］唔好咁易受風向影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691168</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9218655f1c7248a5c14518b942f3d860ba208da7","tid":1691451,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"下次打廢老打手腳啦 頭真係冇用<br />\n打完佢仲企得起 個奸笑仲寒過Joker"},{"pid":"d47db84d7c866a2b73c9961a106b1fa27936fd63","tid":1691451,"uid":238500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27f9592bc6e541f4b727e88ea0ce56aba68fb25","tid":1691451,"uid":150983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:16:20.000Z","msg":"如果用口攔阻嘅可以無視<br />\n但親身攔阻嘅就要當藍絲處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1732dd3866854ad835954076f1001700f8912f6","tid":1691451,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"右膠：拉，分化post"},{"pid":"c9e1c83a0d365d85899fc51064bd31b674a0a9fc","tid":1691451,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"唔好打咬耳仔個大陸人啦，佢一定受到法律制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa973d117d9dfc14b339613ec68bf47e31502ea","tid":1691451,"uid":288673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"成日聽到：夠啦夠啦，打死人啦<br />\n阻膠可唔可以收聲呀<br />\n咁撚鍾意講，阻膠去 POPO 面前講囉"},{"pid":"04691a16c0c13c34c2589db943e567577d3d8565","tid":1691451,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T17:36:59.000Z","msg":"禁住佢將佢手腳屈條係最好 